{"id": 1568, "genre": 1001, "title": "你交往过的人曾经留给你最大的影响是什么？", "description": "仔细想来，前任给你留下了哪些习惯，而你又如何成为今天的你自己？（题图来自：MUTI）", "record_count": 5319, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170314164402WaBO7ujHTqwRvpZl.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-15T03:01:30Z", "options": [{"id": 178688, "content": "不再轻易说喜欢说爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733459}, {"id": 178944, "content": "不要随便就把真心给别人，有可能人家只是玩玩\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971273}, {"id": 179200, "content": "超过北京", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964320}, {"id": 179712, "content": "我喜欢你最初的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903197}, {"id": 178689, "content": "教会她如何温柔，但给了别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970883}, {"id": 178945, "content": "提醒一下卷裤腿那位：这是一生孤单的节奏，不要相信高度能显出来...", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229827}, {"id": 179201, "content": "“生命诚可贵，\n爱情价更高。\n若谓自由故，\n两者皆可抛。”\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971872}, {"id": 179713, "content": "自己要求高了，自己太成熟了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816267}, {"id": 178690, "content": "没有过情侣，但有过交往的朋友曾让我知道了不要因为关系好就一直缠着别人，因为每个人都应该有自己的个人时间和空间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970880}, {"id": 178946, "content": "他告诉我结婚证是红的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600317}, {"id": 179202, "content": "一定要多出去走走 多看看 有很多有趣的人等你去发现", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971874}, {"id": 178691, "content": "在他快射的时候打飞机，一起射。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 77818}, {"id": 178947, "content": "他教会我  不要把你的女/男票当做生活的全部，那只是一部分，你生活的其他方面也极其美好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971262}, {"id": 179203, "content": "最大的影响是她到现在还没有出现", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865217}, {"id": 185091, "content": "学到了不管在什么时候，什么地方，都应该对服务人员说句谢谢?，真的很暖心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986060}, {"id": 178692, "content": "孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834696}, {"id": 178948, "content": "从此好像只被学霸吸引_(:зゝ∠)_ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522021}, {"id": 179204, "content": "不爱你，你干什么都不行。爱你，你干什么都行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971876}, {"id": 179716, "content": "集所有前任的优点于一身，对，就像海绵一样把他们的优点吸收到自己身上", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950657}, {"id": 178693, "content": "留给对方独处空间，距离产生美", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865659}, {"id": 178949, "content": "要努力工作，实现人生价值", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971279}, {"id": 178694, "content": "没有前任 哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956601}, {"id": 178950, "content": "她说我她的师弟告诉她，你得找个有能力的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955405}, {"id": 179206, "content": "她告诉我男人永远忘不了初恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755924}, {"id": 178695, "content": "一个人也挺好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970890}, {"id": 178951, "content": "他做过的一切，让我知道爱一个人应该是什么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833049}, {"id": 184583, "content": "不要太投入", "image": "img/option/option/20170327132627t4AlmsHFweG0RrLj", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984194}, {"id": 188167, "content": "明白不要为了一个人说出违心的话和事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993728}, {"id": 221960, "content": "讓我看清楚自己真正喜歡什麼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078352}, {"id": 224776, "content": "不再爱你真的好难。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914818}, {"id": 178696, "content": "她说我们分开一段时间吧。我说那我们分手吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970359}, {"id": 178952, "content": "为了配得上他努力去变得优秀。虽然依旧没有变优秀也没有在一起，但是保持了一颗要变优秀的上进心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205852}, {"id": 181256, "content": "每个人都有自己的不平凡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976397}, {"id": 178697, "content": "心态放开一点，事情总会有解决的办法，执执念念也不能解决的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967731}, {"id": 178953, "content": "最大限度的理解对方", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721778}, {"id": 179209, "content": "尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091812}, {"id": 179721, "content": "不能心软", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233381}, {"id": 178698, "content": "不要把这个世界想的太美好。要把人想坏一点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590190}, {"id": 178954, "content": "时间长了，她会变成习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971269}, {"id": 178699, "content": "有些人出现在你的生命中，只是为了告诉你，你真的好骗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970537}, {"id": 178955, "content": "没有前任！单身贵族犬一枚???", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710978}, {"id": 179467, "content": "没有交往过的人要怎么回答！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531962}, {"id": 178700, "content": "做好自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965054}, {"id": 178956, "content": "我小时候我哥教我剔牙 刮两颗大门牙 然后过去了将近二十年 我还有这个习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940928}, {"id": 179212, "content": "身体是个小婊渣，男人要对他严格要求，女生嘛就还好啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954428}, {"id": 198157, "content": "想说的话想吐的嘈不要发表给人看，太纸张。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011736}, {"id": 178701, "content": "耍心眼?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970895}, {"id": 178957, "content": "他教会了我，得成熟稳重，向着想要的方向奋斗，没有人会一直包容我，后来我很好，够努力，够坚强，够独立。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955519}, {"id": 179213, "content": "前男友没教会我什么，都是我自学的该如何跟直男相处 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971885}, {"id": 179469, "content": "希望交往过的人都不要成为曾经", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851270}]}